{"tid":2373317,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"香港A貨金仔被指藏有BB彈槍，需每6星期到警署報到！","createTime":"2021-01-20T11:03:16.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-20T12:39:16.000Z","uid":219007,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"1c0f2273d638ec5b4242f66539626f15bbb2f5ac","tid":2373317,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T11:03:16.000Z","msg":"經常以北韓領導人金正恩打扮參與遊行的居港澳洲籍「A貨金正恩」Howard X ，今（20日）在其Facebook專頁發聲明指，去年10月28日遭約10名警察上門搜屋，並以涉嫌無牌管有彈藥將他拘捕，當中涉及BB彈槍；他至今仍未被起訴，但需每6星期到警署報到。他質疑，警方是針對他對中共政府的諷刺，作出的「an arbitrary arrest （任意拘捕）」。<br />\n<br />\nHoward指，當日約有10名警察上門搜屋，並以涉嫌無牌管有彈藥為由將他拘捕，並稱4月份時有一把BB彈槍寄到他家，但Howard稱從未收到警方所指的BB 彈槍。警方搜屋後沒有任何發現後，便將Howard 帶到機場警署。<br />\n<br />\nHoward曾向當時的警方質疑，其拘捕行動是毫無根據，但警方強調命令是來自更高級的部門（the order came from another department higher up），他們只是工作。Howard 又稱，警方曾提到他去年多次出現在遊行或公眾活動現場，例如7.1遊行以及10.1遊行當日他都有出現在IFC，令懷疑這次拘捕根本不是因為BB彈槍。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/uHWFQArSg7m-OnozDinopFy9kd4=/495x606/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/3QK7FBB3IZFCPF5UO7QBV5NRNA.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FuHWFQArSg7m-OnozDinopFy9kd4%3D%2F495x606%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F3QK7FBB3IZFCPF5UO7QBV5NRNA.JPG&h=bc8015c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nHoward認為，其拘捕是由於他過去對中共政府的諷刺性批評，繼而作出的「an arbitrary arrest （任意拘捕）」；續指拘捕不僅為了騷擾他，亦藉此竊取他的指紋及搜屋。他重申，自己尚未被起訴，但需每6星期到警署報到。<br />\n《蘋果》已就事件向警方查詢，正等候回覆。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210120/2HWBK25YYNCEJAQAE2B5XTOTAE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210120%2F2HWBK25YYNCEJAQAE2B5XTOTAE%2F&d=6tm4WXRLZYcZc%2BeJmW1IayMX%2BuEjOoKUanh%2Bi4Xf2cM%3D&h=df37c073\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210120%2F2HWBK25YYNCEJAQAE2B5XTOTAE%2F&h=43dd1bc6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210120/2HWBK25YYNCEJAQAE2B5XTOTAE/</a>"},{"pid":"b6f89c4d863297bd1e2a03a83aaf56f04f469915","tid":2373317,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T11:08:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed8b2fb94ccd31ca77aa761c1bd3f376f9cc8ec1","tid":2373317,"uid":39710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T11:09:08.000Z","msg":"癡癡地"},{"pid":"0625b964457c07b44eb4c0ab9a1825b545eeb124","tid":2373317,"uid":7050,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T11:15:02.000Z","msg":"佢好似鐘意拜登架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d2b1e02d376d8c87828b3e621bbacfe5e0d993b","tid":2373317,"uid":227588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T11:18:11.000Z","msg":"啱啱瞓醒，廣華街封鋪抄家未？"},{"pid":"d69fb983d58f02d0c4014cdfc46bc701a31a5093","tid":2373317,"uid":101994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T12:16:57.000Z","msg":"Rfa有片<br />\n拎導彈入狗屋 好好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://fb.watch/37RWoIL5Ik/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffb.watch%2F37RWoIL5Ik%2F&d=6tm4WXRLZYcZc%2BeJmW1IayMX%2BuEjOoKUanh%2Bi4Xf2cM%3D&h=1f7c174d\" target=\"_blank\">https://fb.watch/37RWoIL5Ik/</a>"},{"pid":"d50690923c9e8f0eb0a968d3e75f7b182289e1c0","tid":2373317,"uid":289257,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0625b964457c07b44eb4c0ab9a1825b545eeb124","tid":2373317,"uid":7050,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T11:15:02.000Z","msg":"佢好似鐘意拜登架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T12:19:30.000Z","msg":"撐敗燈畀狗拉抵佢死<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class